Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最後成了件大工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不感到懷念嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會把這個拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:25.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會不知道這是多麼危險的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在看護著它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:37.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此才會成那些孩子今後旅途上需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因果循環啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:42.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管人類看起來像是重複同樣的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但因果絶不是循環的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是螺旋般的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:57.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子不一定會選如你我一樣的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:01.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:10.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的靈力竟如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:13.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,結界輕而易舉就被擊破了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要為我而戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但無論哪條路我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此才要心平氣和地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:33.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:51.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至少最後能再一次看到你那羞澀的笑容
Comment: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.34,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START--------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才一瞬間好像感受到了師傅的念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望快點得到芙羅拉的誇獎而按捺不住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:40.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女見習卻能退治惡鬼定會成為這裡的新傳說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的只是堵住獸鬼的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然召喚出了巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不能好好使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,徒然讓損害擴大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你的眼睛有點可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:16.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說我還不知道他們是不是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個寺院傷口沒有癒合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:34.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然傷口已經癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 傷口非常深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉體的傷口確實癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但幽體的傷口還留在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放任不管就會不斷衰弱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚會讓肉體的傷口再次裂開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 能救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:05:00.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,儘快抬到洋館 讓他服下師傅的靈藥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家來幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是一時沒站穩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀倒是可以借你一用 雖然我不情願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:23.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幽體之傷即精神之傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會有法忍受的劇痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的人都無法保持意識清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:31.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們逃出以後在那裡到底遇到了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:40.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傷應該不是獸鬼弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:45.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我施上去的護符也不知什麼時候被抹消了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是用它揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:54.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用這東西揍了自認為是天使的怪物一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這種 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,區區人類竟有和那種高位靈體戰鬥的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:11.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷斬殺幽體而獲得此種力量的劍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因被預言的奇蹟而蒙蔽雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:22.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請看看眼前的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:26.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這種靈氣的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是洋館的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的結界消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞和卡思嘉在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是剩下的獸鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有棘手的東西在洋館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼根本不能比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師 師博大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快攔住她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋從哪冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:55.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 有人類闖入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要揮動那把大劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:07.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻搖搖晃晃地 真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是你 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:24.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我和這個洋館的主人交情很深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 所以那時會在獸鬼的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些使徒不配知我名諱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:41.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只會說給向5名天使復仇之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼胡言亂語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等這樣啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我等之主轉生之時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,於該地現身的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們主人的祭品 那個倖存下來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:12.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟會在這裡遇到你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說你們的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不問也知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:30.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,命定為主君的在這世上只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就委派給我古倫貝路多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:43.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽過你的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是一介凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是從他的蝕中生還的豪傑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:02.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人多勢眾攻打一個在如此偏僻的森林隱居的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,實在有損武人的名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:12.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是向鷹示忠的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,於是本人才要求與他們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會遇到你這樣的武者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,著沉重的步伐來到此地也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯的命令 為何他要把婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:35.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我古倫貝路多 特作為鷹之團的一介武夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑色劍士單挑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼鷹之團
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法怎麼了 魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的心很亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使不出魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個快從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用你的羽毛羽毛撢子做點什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:24.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 只會把火勢增大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:28.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人 你在哪 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽著 我的嫡傳弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個交給黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是 莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:50.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快些 可怕的敵人迫近了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去劍士先生會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣的話師傅你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻已來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣 這樣太殘忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,應該更寧靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被這樣的火包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:17.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我本就背負的這樣的罪業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:23.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人類違背時間的法則延命至今是多麼罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:28.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身為魔法師的你應該清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 果然還是太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:42.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不管是陽光下的膝枕 還是和格雷姆們的午茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有 所有都會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都要被燒毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼凶狠的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還是人類的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,力量卻高於一般的使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:21.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有什麼資格 自稱鷹之團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:36.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 剛才亂來那麼一下裂了好幾根骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的劍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:44.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了我兩戰錘竟然沒有斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你這算什麼戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:53.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,連抵抗都不行 只是一直被打飛不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,站著說話不腰疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,連甲冑都沒有赤膊上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍老大也是真喜歡這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也趕緊做完工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把魔女的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你他媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做這傢伙的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙把同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:29.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令 你們把魔女的腦袋帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正打得火熱的時候 你要去追女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:47.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說 戰鬥才是一切 不死者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:54.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要會錯意 能阻止你的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:02.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都和平時不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 喔 都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女的弟子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:14.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 剛退冶了獸鬼 這次是怪人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:21.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們不想死就告訴我魔女在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就是說了也會被燒死罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不趕緊跑出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很殘酷 但是要去救芙羅拉的話我們也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去寶物庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有必須交給格斯的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這就是師傅的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:59.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是不是我的命運 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在能救他的只有我這個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有身為靈樹森林的魔女芙羅拉的弟子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:13.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要給的東西 是那個護符嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對 但不止這些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅上了護符的咒物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險且強力的某種咒物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是那個黑色劍士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說打敗了不少使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:46.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個不死的左德打的不分上下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的宿敵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是這種窩囊廢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德大人運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇上那種勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對武者來說 戰場即是聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,置於死地而後生才是本分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:16.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你好像不配武者的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個怪物現在裝什麼武者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自我陶醉的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:30.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作為戰士 你不配死在我戰錘之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,化為碎片消散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:52.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,切 大隻的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要進到哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是要命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像史爾基說的 傷口裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我處理不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 這樣就算穿上那個也動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拖拖拉拉的 火就要燒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:45.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,的確現在這個狀態穿上那個還能保命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:46.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 魔女在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 是那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡果然還是要靠的我的魔法撐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:04.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是把大家捲入危險的我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給傷成這樣的格斯穿上甲冑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能相信史爾基了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在哪裡了 黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還要醜態百出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明應該咬死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:44.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這不光是厲害了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才還都站不起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這就不厚道了 這麼厲害的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在退治獸鬼的時候就該給他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:57.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是那麼簡單的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從動作上看完全變了個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 那把劍確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很懷念啊 老友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也要讓他踏上同樣的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一樣化為冥府魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這甲胃是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:30.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上的時候 傷口就像假的一樣不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛都 無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這股在體內沸騰的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:52.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體中有什麼 狂暴的東西湧現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 身 體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 血 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:57.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 一 切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 骨 髓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上你的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 生 命
